{"tid":720963,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"平心而論，論表現睇係伊朗🇮🇷個龍勁定南韓🇰🇷個龍勁啲先","createTime":"2018-06-28T10:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T08:48:39.000Z","uid":92376,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b51abc0169dba7d51fa139b70e5f49f2088e8d7","tid":720963,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"伊朗 神救牙朗十二碼 失既兩球波都唔係佢可以救到 手力驚人開生波一野掟到過半場 背景夠勵志，由瞓街到做國腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南韓 一輸十二碼就收皮 身手靈活度同伊朗打和 貪靚踢波都要化妝似做明星多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔明啲人不停吹奏韓國個龍做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算要去歐洲發展都係比朗芬先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iran.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iran.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iran.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00417919b9e9b96e97c9eb0a01145f0381c7610f","tid":720963,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca9ade8ada2a25af9043353b4588054a87d827e1","tid":720963,"uid":62073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:46:44.000Z","msg":"韓國個龍夠mk有話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n好似化左妝白到<br />\n但遲d要服兵役了，鬼外流到<br />\n<br />\n伊朗龍有機外流，e.g. 俄超果d<br />\n撲出C朗12m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f6776fa4b78b945e383196c3cecfe99aa31482","tid":720963,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00417919b9e9b96e97c9eb0a01145f0381c7610f","tid":720963,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi